Description: Digital photograph (colour); view of engraved rock art showing human figure and figure of dog, both upright and facing right, pecked in outline. Human figure is infilled with pecking and face on, with outstretched arms, left hand holding straight object, right hand holding curved object. Dog is to right. 10cm photo scale fitted at base of image. Aswan, Egypt. Scanned
Acquisition name: Donated by: Trust for African Rock Art
